This project is part of the CodSoft Data Science Internship. The goal is to build a machine learning model that predicts the rating of a movie based on various features such as genre, director, actors, duration, and votes.

Movie rating prediction is a regression problem where the model learns patterns from historical movie data and estimates ratings for new movies.

